{{Top|leg}}
The '''holy yacht''' was the private [[Starship/Legends|vessel]] of [[Shimrra Jamaane]], the [[Supreme Overlord]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. When Shimrra sent the [[Yuuzhan Vong fleet|Yuuzhan Vong armada]] to [[Defense of Mon Calamari (Yuuzhan Vong War)|attack]] the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] capital world of [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]], the vessel was coated with sacrificial blood, and wrought with wreaths of thorn-vine and fans sacred to [[Yun-Yammka]]. The vessel also contained a special [[villip]] which could contact any other villip, whether dedicated or choir, all at once.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

